NEUTROPHIL

The average fold change of gene expression from baseline and p-value are calculated for each gene. ***

The Volcano plot displays p-value and fold change for each gene. Marked are the genes with p-value > .01 and fold change > 1.3 to identify those which might play a role during fistula remodeling and adaption.

The number of genes with larger expression variation is equal to 42; the list of genes is saved under “Significant”.
